    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若是发现对方举止异常，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者感觉自己的安全遭到威胁，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就请按下面前的按钮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>犯人会立即遭到处决。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030980/extras/bcf73c21f35ce4e91532106690b0c3a7.poster.avif?t=1769612449\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030980/extras/bcf73c21f35ce4e91532106690b0c3a7.webm?t=1769612449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030980/extras/bcf73c21f35ce4e91532106690b0c3a7.mp4?t=1769612449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特征</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1次游戏大概需要5分钟。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只需点击即可完成绝大部分操作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摆在眼前的红色按钮就是「处决开关」。<br>你可以在任何时候自由地按下按钮，即使是在对话途中。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按或不按、何时按下、选择肢都会改变剧情。<br>玩家的选择、好奇心与自责将衍生出总共13种不同的结局。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重制版的变化</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作品是以2023年10月免费公布在<br>Unityroom上的原版为基础的重制版本。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为「米拉」添加完整语音</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新增几个结局，以及与之相应的BGM、CG与立绘</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新增Steam成就系统支持</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新增画廊模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新增英语、简繁中文支持</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >配音</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >米拉：菜月なこ</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制作人员</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序、剧本：Indigo Ingots</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美术：polaritia</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐：Kazura's MUSIC</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >提醒</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直播时请在说明栏注明游戏标题与本网页的链接。</p>",
